description:
WNBA and New York Liberty star Sabrina Ionescu joins the show this week to talk shop with Matt and Stak. Sabrina opens up about her relationship with Kobe and discusses his impact on her game. Plus, she discusses her WNBA career so far, her time at Oregon, relationship with Steph Curry and much more.
